        <p>• Improve ATM touch screen quality, sensitivity, and clarity by partnering up with a manufacturer to design a
          new ATM. </p>
        <p>• Create a clean user interface to convey ease of access and peace of mind when using Bitstop ATMs by:</p>
        <p><span style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 1.125rem;">- Updating the user flow to include scam
            warning screens and other security measures, preventing users from sending Bitcoin to the wrong
            wallet.</span></p>
        <p><span style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 1.125rem;">- Adding clearly visible information on all
            fees and updated Bitcoin prices to keep the transaction process transparent.</span></p>
        <p>- Adding a welcome dashboard and clear tier system to streamline the user experience, helping minimize
          possible confusion among users.</p>
        <p>• Connect ATMs to a backend dashboard for franchisees, giving network partners more control over their own
          kiosks.</p>
        <p>• Reduce the number of negative reviews through a combination of the redesigned UI, easy to follow on-screen
          instructions, and clear information on fees and Bitcoin conversion rates.</p>
