            <p>As the face of our ATMs, I wanted the home screen to be bold and eye catching. We went through a few
              iterations to make sure we hit all our goals.&nbsp;</p>
            <p>1. As a company with global ambitions it was important to find a space for the inclusion of language
              selection.&nbsp;</p>
            <p>2. We wanted to bring as much transparency as possible up front with a info button by the bitcoin price
              to learn more. Clicking on it brings up a popup where users can simulate what their receipt would look
              like based on the amount inserted before they begin checkout.&nbsp;</p>
            <p>3. It was also a priority for us to make sure users know they need and have a bitcoin wallet before they
              begin for a smooth checkout process. Therefore we offered an easy way to download a recommended wallet
              right from the home screen.&nbsp;</p>
            <p>4. Our website, social, and support needed to be easily visible to drive traffic to our website, gain
              following on social, and be there for our customers if they were to have any questions even before they
              begin checkout.</p>
